  <h2>Introduction</h2>
  <p>ZimEduFinder (“we”, “our”, “us”) operates https://skoolfinder.net (the “Site”). This Privacy Policy explains what personal data we collect, how we use it, how we protect it, and the choices you have.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <h3>1.1 Account information</h3>
  <p>When you sign in using Google or Facebook we collect:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Name</li>
    <li>Email address (if provided by the provider)</li>
    <li>Profile photo URL</li>
    <li>Provider-specific identifier (Google/Facebook ID)</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>1.2 Preferences & usage</h3>
  <p>We store search preferences, selected filters, saved favourite schools, and basic usage analytics to improve recommendations.</p>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To provide and personalise school recommendations</li>
    <li>To save your preferences and favourites</li>
    <li>To communicate with you about your requests and account</li>
    <li>To analyse and improve Site performance</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Sharing & Third Parties</h2>
  <p>We do not sell your personal data. We may share information with third-party providers who help operate the Site (e.g. MongoDB Atlas, authentication providers). These providers process data under their own privacy policies.</p>

  <h2>4. Security</h2>
  <p>We use HTTPS, access controls and secure storage. While we take reasonable steps to protect data, no internet service is completely secure.</p>

  <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You may request access, correction or deletion of your personal data. See <a href="/data-deletion">Data Deletion Instructions</a> for how to delete your account.</p>

  <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
  <p>We retain personal data for as long as your account exists or as necessary to provide services, comply with legal obligations, or resolve disputes.</p>

  <h2>7. Contact</h2>
  <p>If you have questions, email <a href="mailto:support@skoolfinder.net">support@skoolfinder.net</a>.</p>

  <hr />
  <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#777">ZimEduFinder — ZimEduFinder respects your privacy. This policy may be updated; the date above shows the last update.</p>
